reviews.text: A good place to find all the stuffing would like to buy. An upscale supermarket
reasonably priced upscale supermarket at basement 2 of hysan place, do check out the urban bakery too!
Opens late (closes around 12), super convenient location (on top of mtr) and a great selection of foods.
Great selection of goods and food. Wide range of deli and great services with health and beauty mannings stores located nearby

Decent selection as more sensible prices than most places.  The staff are really friendly and always willing to get you a shopping cart, answer questions about the food  or even get you something fresh our of boxes they are unpacking.  It's necessary to read the pack and check produce to be sure you get the best quality as it's quite mixed.

reviews.text:
コズウェイベイで、スーパーをあんまり考えていなかったので、じっくり観ていなかったのが盲点でした。
太古のイオンまで遠出して買っているものがいくつかありました。

☆納豆、種類的には太古のイオンと変わりません。

☆キムチ、太古のイオンより非常に種類があります。大葉のキムチとか、二十日大根のキムチなど他で買えないキムチがあります。

☆インスタントラーメン、キムチの種類が豊富だったので、見てみると韓国のインスタントラーメン、カップラーメンともに充実していました。

☆フランス製角砂糖、いつもは近所のフュージョンで買うのですが、ここにも売っていました。

もう少し、じっくり今度様子を見て買い物をしたいと思います。

コズウェイベイのそごう百貨店の近くと、言う事で日本人に人気の買い物エリアであるのが影響しているかもしれません。

☆追記
お昼頃お買い物をして、デリバリーを頼んだら午後３時頃には配達がありました。梱包も丁寧だし。配達員も好印象です。。
是超級市場，地方寬敞，環境舒適，品種繁多。工作人員服務質数良好，禮貌待客，服務週到。  另設有日本拉麵檔、咖啡店、寿司店的服務，供遊人享用、休息。
A good place to find all the stuffing would like to buy. An upscale supermarket
很多貨品，選擇很多。
冷氣好足夠

reviews.text:
One of many malls dotting Causeway Bay area. Its lobby has a high vertical clearance. Trendy crowd...maybe because there was an Avengers exhibition going on at the time of my visit.

Had some difficulty finding Marketplace but as it turned out, was called Jasons, which is located two floors below ground.

The building had separate entries for the shopping areas and the office/residential area.
Amazing department store with all that you need in it. Great shops and restaurants
Large shopping mall in central location, not easy or pleasant to walk around or navigate. There are better malls in HK.

The big bookstore alone is worthy for a visit. The food court is decent and the general selection of stores is nicely put together. Directly connected to the mass transit too so this location is hard to beat.

Great shopping mall with can different kind of shops, including fashion, books store, restaurants, and Apple store.
Unlike other shopping mall, their escalator can easily reach each floor.
And there is a sky garden located on 4/F, which is a great place for relaxing, and it's open from 10am to 10pm
